title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: When it comes to multi-tasking, you can hold your own among the very best. Your juggling skills are clearly evident when you simultaneously play the role of both student and teacher today. Sharing what you know with those you respect is a privilege too wonderful to pass up, and so is the opportunity to absorb the lessons your experiences and interactions teach. You can make carrying one, two, or even three trains of thought at a time look easy now. Your mental agility is a gift that keeps on giving. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
